data.description: $4500 SELLER CONCESSION!!!!! LARGE CORNER LOT!  Beautiful East facing home that sits on a large corner lot with a eye-catching retaining wall on the North side.  Inviting entrance from the courtyard to the spacious and open great room.  Neutral colors and natural light both make for a lovely home to entertain family and friends. Split-bedroom floor-plan. Master suite offers 2 spacious walk-in closets, double vanity, walk-in shower and soaking tub.  The backyard offers privacy, a covered patio and it backs to a common area.  The over-sized garage has work-space and room for storage.  Great opportunity to live in the beautiful SW and are only 20 minutes from downtown.
